TextEng: "There is another name I wish to know."
"The Puzzle Ring and the Sensei's Amulet? They may have them."
Text: "퍼즐 반지와 선사의 호신부? 그들이 가지고 있을지도 몰라."

TextEng: "Speak Mephistopheles' True Name, Phyreshi the Knower!"
"Yes, here is the 500,000 gold the gods demand."
Text: "그래, 신들이 요구하는 금화 50만 개가 여기 있어."

TextEng: "Yes, here is the 200,000 gold the gods demand."
Text: "그래, 신들이 요구하는 금화 20만 개가 여기 있어."

TextEng: "Yes, here is the 100,000 gold the gods demand."
Text: "그래, 신들이 요구하는 금화 10만 개가 여기 있어."

TextEng: "Yes, here is the 300,000 gold the gods demand."

TextEng: "Phew! They're more hassle than they're worth anyway."
Text: "휴! 어차피 받을 만한 가치보다 더 귀찮아."

TextEng: "Someone I don't yet know? Is that true?"
"Thank you, Knower. His name is music to my ears."
Text: "고마워, 현자. 그의 이름은 내 귀에 음악 같아."

TextEng: "Someone I don't yet know? Is that true?"
"She's the Sleeping Man's true love as well!"
"She is soft and kind and weak!"
"She's dead! She's become one of the Lost!"
Text: "그녀는 죽었어! 잃어버린 자들 중 하나가 됐어!"

TextEng: "She's the Sleeping Man's true love as well!"
"Thank you, Knower. Her name is music to my ears."
Text: "고마워, 현자. 그녀의 이름은 내 귀에 음악 같아."

TextEng: "That of the Sleeping Man's one true love..."
"Yes, here is the 300,000 gold the gods demand."
Text: "그래, 신들이 요구하는 금화 30만 개가 여기 있어."

TextEng: "That's wonderful! Return with me at once so we can tell him!"
Text: "멋져! 당장 나랑 같이 돌아가서 그에게 말해주자!"

TextEng: "But you are his one true love!"
"Phyreshi the Knower, I command you to go to the Sleeping Man!"
"Barred to you? Return with me at once and you shall see him!"
Text: "금지됐다고? 당장 나랑 같이 돌아가면 그를 볼 수 있어!"

TextEng: "The Knower of Places? Is that true?"
"It just doesn't seem like a good fit."
"That's wonderful! I must return to tell him!"
"That's horrible! This can't be happening to me!"
Text: "끔찍해! 나한테 이런 일이 일어날 수 없어!"

TextEng: "He's a bloody angel, for crying out loud!"
"That's wonderful! I must return to tell him!"
"Yes, here is the 100,000 gold the gods demand."
Text: "그래, 신들이 요구하는 금화 10만 개가 여기 있어."

TextEng: "Yes, here is the 200,000 gold the gods demand."
Text: "그래, 신들이 요구하는 금화 20만 개가 여기 있어."

TextEng: "Yes, here is the 200,000 gold the gods demand."
Text: "그래, 신들이 요구하는 금화 20만 개가 여기 있어."

TextEng: "Yes, here is the 200,000 gold the gods demand."
Text: "그래, 신들이 요구하는 금화 20만 개가 여기 있어."

TextEng: "I must return to the City of Lost Souls. Can you get me there?"
Text: "잃어버린 영혼들의 도시로 돌아가야 해. 나를 그곳으로 보내줄 수 있어?"

TextEng: "How long have you been imprisoned here?"
"A False Rebellion? What do you mean?"
"And what role did you play in this False Rebellion?"
Text: "이 거짓 반란에서 당신은 어떤 역할을 했어?"

TextEng: "Who was this Baron and why did he bring them doom?"
Text: "이 남작은 누구고 왜 그들에게 파멸을 가져온 거야?"

TextEng: "Why do you call me Scourge of Cania?"
"Why do you call me Judge of Cania?"
"Why do you call me Light of Cania?"
"You must be mistaken. My name is <FullName>."
"Thank you, Knower. Her name is music to my ears."
Text: "고마워, 현자. 그녀의 이름은 내 귀에 음악 같아."

TextEng: "Thank you, Knower. Her name is music to my ears."
Text: "고마워, 현자. 그녀의 이름은 내 귀에 음악 같아."

TextEng: "Thank you, Knower. His name is music to my ears."
Text: "고마워, 현자. 그의 이름은 내 귀에 음악 같아."
